Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning. Wakey wakey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Myu. Good morning. I'll get up now,\Nso please stop slapping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime... Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, why are you and\NBig Sister Yue always naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand once you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll understand when I grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, do you understand\Nbecause this part of you grew up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have one.\NWill I never understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu, listen. It's normal that you\Ndon't have this because you're a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:02:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't need to,\Nfor at least 10 years... No, 20 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, it's something you must\Nnot have anything to do with, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu, everyone cooked\Nbreakfast for you this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a full-course fish meal,\Nyour favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So both of you, get dressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this isn't good for Myu's education!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been six days since we got back\Nfrom the Sunken Ruins of Melusine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've clearly stayed too long.\NWe need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, what are we doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... I'm going to\Nmake some new equipment, or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, what shall I make today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're going to play tag today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're all chasing after you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, good luck getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here we go! Stop right there!\N--Stop where you are, Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really need to get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I tell Myu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll definitely cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want you to live\Na sad life where you cut ties
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with everyone and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is on you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?! Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this is part of the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give it back, Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I did\Nanything to deserve thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're spending so much effort\Nthinking about my daughter's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a mother, I can't help\Nbut express my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew.\NI was kind of trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Everyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It also seems like the ladies are\Nalso thinking the same thing, too.\N--Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Stealing is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad Myu met such wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all done so much for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't concern yourself over this.\NDo what you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After meeting you, she grew up so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be such a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now she can think\Nabout others, beyond herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She also knows that you have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still very young, so she does\Ntend to fall back on being a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, she's never said,\N"Don't go," has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She understands that\Nshe can't keep you here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let a child\Nconcern herself over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll tell her clearly\Nthat we're leaving tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nwe'll prepare a feast tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a farewell party for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, please don't call me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remia, you have guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remia-{\i1}san{\i0}, since when...\NI can't let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, depending on the angle, it could look\Nlike she is performing a certain service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing it in public, that's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}? Can I have my swimsuit back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0},\Ndid Papa ask you to steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, you just had to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime, have mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too! If you want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, in that case, mine too.\NTop or bottom? Or both?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Remia-{\i1}san{\i0}, not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see each other anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, will you always be my Papa,\Neven if we're apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want, Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll say, safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, one day, I'll go pick you up later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu, I'm going somewhere\Nvery far away. So--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you can go, Papa, I can go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm Papa's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once everything is over,\NI'll come back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring everyone\Nwith me to come see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really. Have I ever lied to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I come back, I'll take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can see my hometown,\Nwhere I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where Papa grew up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be surprised.\NMy hometown is like a jack-in-the-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking forward to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then be good and wait with your mom.\NDon't do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to your mom\Nand help around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, what about Mama? Can she come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't leave me out, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess, but... It's seriously\Na completely different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I not follow\Nmy daughter and husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Myu, please help prepare for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking her along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you've decided, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a bit unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I thought, given how you are now,\Nyou'd just say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did meeting Myu change you a bit, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if you\Ncouldn't choose the timing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you found a way to go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it might not be a method that\Nyou can use whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return to Myu no matter what,\Nand I will show her Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I cross worlds without Myu, I'll just\Nhave to do whatever it takes to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can cross worlds as\Nmany times as we need. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, being ignored like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will treasure this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have the same one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Myu. All right, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe trip to you, too, big sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, we promise we'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be good until we come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just that. Father\Nhas been acting strangely, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody here that I can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the preparations\Nare finally complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I've been\Nwaiting for is finally upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do to my students,\Nby locking me up like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything shall be as he wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you have left the board,\Nthere is no need for you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come if you dare, Irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the end of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The oracle has spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lord, the voice of\Nour god himself, has issued his decree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall destroy the infidels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them know his divine will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them feel our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let those fools who act like\Nthey control the northern continent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,understand their proper place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This phenomenon that's\Nbeen spreading in the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "Void" that is making knights and\Nsoldiers feel lethargic. What is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything in order, Jose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, nobody saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large part of the army,\Nincluding the leader and officers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are showing signs of\Nbeing affected by the "Void."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty percent of the\Narmed forces of Heiligh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really some sort of attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they just all being unfocused--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose, it could get you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, commander?\NHow is the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is currently not showing\Nany signs of the "Void."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, he is getting more\Nand more energized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will punish the barbarism of the\NDemons, under the name of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose, gather those\Nwith knowledge of Dark Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have them investigate\Nthe true nature of the "Void"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have them prepare countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. What about\NKouki-{\i1}kun {\i0}and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will talk to them.\NRight now, they're unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to agitate them\Nif I don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I suppose it's inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that affects only morale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be natural to assume\Nthe Demons are behind this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A direct attack on\Nthe royal palace? Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If such a thing were possible,\Nwhy not use a more powerful magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can use magic without being\Ndetected, why not go after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing the Knight Commander\Nwould surely damage morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he's doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let this letter make it to Duke\NZengen of Ankaji and to Hajime Nagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Commander Meld.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Hiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuke? What's going on,\Nand at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I... There's something\NI really need to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I know it's asking for a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't want\Nmy classmates to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... No, it's not asking for a lot.\NGo ahead, let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can work out what\Nthe problem is together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an urgent report\NI need to deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Commander Meld.\NI'll wait outside until you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thanks, Daisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he brainwashed? I hope you\Ndon't mind getting a bit hurt, Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuke, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Howl, all winds--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, "A Disturbing Darkness."